Module wgu.softwareproject
Package wgu.softwareproject

Class Part

java.lang.Object
wgu.softwareproject.Part
Direct Known Subclasses:
InHouse, Outsourced
public abstract class Part extends Object
This is the Part abstract superclass that is extended when In-house or Outsourced parts are initialized.
